## Step 4: Calculate the final fixed assets net value

The calculation is:

Initial value: 8,000,000.00
Additional fixed assets: 2,670,827.47
Accumulated depreciation: 127,633.22

Final fixed assets net value = 8,000,000.00 + 2,670,827.47 - 127,633.22 = 10,543,194.25
